CITY OF INDUSTRY , CALIFORNIA City of Industry , or simply referred to as Industry , is an industrial suburb of Los Angeles in the San Gabriel Valley region of Los Angeles County , California .
Home to over 2,500 businesses and 80,000 jobs , but only 219 residents according to the 2010 census ( down from 777 residents in 2000 ) , the city is almost entirely industrial .
It was incorporated on June 18 , 1957 to prevent surrounding cities from annexing industrial land for tax revenue .
